             </dlentry>
         </dl>
            <dl>
                <dlentry>
                    <dt>sdcFunctions</dt>
                    <dd>An object that runs functions that evaluate or modify data. Includes the
                        following methods: </dd>
                    <dd>
                        <ul id="ul_sps_ykc_d1b">
                            <li
                                conref="../Reusable_Content/ReusablePhrases.dita#concept_vhs_5tz_xp/li_getFieldNull"
